{"tid":294450,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"[Acer JJ] 自從加左SSD同Ram之後，成日Boot唔到機","createTime":"2017-06-23T03:18:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-24T19:08:44.000Z","uid":34181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0c020a68cdeb9dfe43a3982e369455547eea48b2","tid":294450,"uid":34181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T03:18:51.000Z","msg":"之前見部Acer Vn7-591G開始變慢，<br />\n自己郁手拆機，加左條8G Ram同M.2 SSD。<br />\n點知依排開機個陣，成日話No bootable device.<br />\n但係每次用Ctrl+alt+del大法Reboot一次又開到機。<br />\n<br />\n我有試過重插HDD條線，<br />\n(因為個win10裝左係HDD<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n但係個問題都係解決唔到。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有冇巴打知唔知咩原因？"},{"pid":"ded28cc8ed969b9579e03ad535f972a1420d08f1","tid":294450,"uid":108085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T06:10:43.000Z","msg":"你win 10要装係ssd"},{"pid":"19952e9cdbff2dcf26a6c3443ce1fea578187194","tid":294450,"uid":34181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T11:52:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你win 10要装係ssd</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我試過將HDD clone完落SSD之後，<br />\n開機Run唔到隻Windows，<br />\n都係話No bootable device。<br />\n所以我之後都冇搞落去，<br />\n用番HDD做System disk算。"},{"pid":"d6ac6bbb09d3a5e99d4d9c590efbe504ba4e3d27","tid":294450,"uid":57677,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T01:49:10.000Z","msg":"唔好 clone, 我用全新裝"},{"pid":"5186e1efbf7a52ce75e786a0205b5a828f30a605","tid":294450,"uid":97059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T19:07:44.000Z","msg":"重裝嘅話齋插 ssd 裝，裝好先插返 ssd"},{"pid":"e7428d1ee68d752227c762df6f20d689e1c4e9be","tid":294450,"uid":97059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T19:08:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>重裝嘅話齋插 ssd 裝，裝好先插返 <del>ssd</del><span style=\"color: red;\">hdd</span></blockquote>"}]}